com.nokia.maps.kml

Interface StyleMap


  • public interface StyleMap
    This interface represents the <StyleMap> tag from KML specification. A <StyleMap> maps between two different Styles. Typically a <StyleMap> element is used to provide separate normal and highlighted styles for a <Placemark>, so that the highlighted version appears when the user mouses over the icon. 

    
 <StyleMap id="ID">
    
   <Pair id="ID">
    
       <key>normal or highlight </key> 
    
      <styleUrl>...</styleUrl> or <Style>...</Style> 
    
   </Pair>
    
 </StyleMap>
